thread.title: Les Jarvis
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Les Jarvis

author: Les Jarvis
title: Les Jarvis
text:
I have just purchased a set of inks for my Canon printer.
My previous purchase from a well known electrical retailer cost me $170.00 for the set of 5 inks. I found INK STATION on line and purchased the same genuine inks for $84.92 a saving of $85.08. They were delivered the next day. Now that's what I call service. I know where I will get my inks from in future, and I will not hesitate to recommend INK STATION to my friends
Well Done
Les J
